creator: Turtle Shell Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Dozee App is for configuration and data visualization of Dozee device. Dozee is your personal non-wearable health monitoring device. All you need to do is simply slide it under your mattress and Dozee device will automatically track your sleep pattern and body vitals.

Dozee is an AI-based contactless health monitor with remote monitoring and alert system. Dozee
works on Ballistocardiography - a scientific method that measures the micro and macro
vibrations produced by our heartbeats, respiration and body movements. The sensor sheet has
piezoelectric sensors in it which track the mechanical vibrations produced by the body. It can
even collect details of heart valve functionality. These micro-vibrations in the form of electric
signals are analyzed by AI-based algorithms to monitor a person’s health-biomarkers on a
regular basis. Any deviation is provided to clinicians as an alert that they can quickly act upon.
Dozee’s accuracy is validated against a gold standard - Polysomnography and ECG at highly
reputed research institutes and hospitals.

Features:
Get Early Alerts - With Dozee Advanced Health Intelligence (AHI), get life saving alerts even before symptoms show
Regular Health Reports - Daily, Weekly, Monthly reports as well as reports for Sleep Apnea & Cardiac Performance on the mobile app
Remote Health Monitoring - Stay on top of your loved ones health from anywhere
Consult with the Experts - Chat with our panel of experts for any health-related queries
De-stress with Meditation Library - World’s first AI-powered meditation assistant and Sleep Music Library to relax and unwind
Earn Health with Dozee - Earn points every time you sleep & meditate, redeem for products and services from top wellness brands to get healthier
Dozee app integration with Health app (HealthKit)-

Sleep analysis

title: Dozee

creator: Turtle Shell Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Dozee App is for analyzing vitals, stress & sleep data from the Dozee device, exploring self-care solutions such as meditation & sleep music and health coaching. Dozee device, India’s 1st contactless health companion, is an AI-based contactless health monitor with remote monitoring and alert system. Dozee works on Ballistocardiography - a scientific method that measures the micro and macro vibrations produced by our heartbeats, respiration and body movements. These micro-vibrations in the form of electric signals are analyzed by AI-based algorithms to monitor a person’s health-biomarkers on a regular basis. Any deviation is provided to clinicians as an alert that they can quickly act upon. Dozee App is for configuration of the Dozee device and analyzing the data of yourself or your loved ones from anywhere in the world. The app also has self-care solutions in the form of different types of relaxation and meditation solutions, blogs and sleep music for problems identified from the data.

Features:
Get Early Alerts - With Dozee Advanced Health Intelligence (AHI), get life saving alerts even before symptoms show
Regular Health Reports - Daily, Weekly, Monthly reports as well as reports for Sleep Apnea on the mobile app
Remote Health Monitoring - Stay on top of your loved ones health from anywhere
Consult with the Experts - Chat with our panel of experts for any health-related queries
De-stress with Meditation Library - World’s first AI-powered meditation assistant and Sleep Music Library to relax and unwind
Earn Health with Dozee - Earn points every time you sleep & meditate, redeem for products and services from top wellness brands to get healthier
Dozee app integration with Health app (HealthKit)-
Heart rate
Respiration rate
Sleep analysis

Read more about Dozee at https://www.dozee.io

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Introducing Vitals Mode with SpO2 for day-time tracking. Now don’t just monitor your vitals in your sleep. Track your vitals during the day by just lying above your Dozee device with medical-grade accuracy. With Dozee SpO2, also track and analyze your blood oxygen levels from time-to-time.

Dozee device, India’s 1st contactless health companion, is an AI-based contactless health monitor with remote monitoring and alert system. Dozee works on Ballistocardiography - a scientific method that measures the micro and macro vibrations produced by our heartbeats, respiration and body movements. These micro-vibrations in the form of electric signals are analyzed by AI-based algorithms to monitor a person’s health-biomarkers on a regular basis. Any deviation is provided to clinicians as an alert that they can quickly act upon. Dozee App is for configuration of the Dozee device and analyzing the data of yourself or your loved ones from anywhere in the world. The app also has self-care solutions in the form of different types of relaxation and meditation solutions, blogs and sleep music for problems identified from the data.

Features:
Get Early Alerts - With Dozee Advanced Health Intelligence (AHI), get life saving alerts even before symptoms show
Regular Health Reports - Daily, Weekly, Monthly reports as well as reports for Sleep Apnea on the mobile app
Remote Health Monitoring - Stay on top of your loved ones health from anywhere
Consult with the Experts - Chat with our panel of experts for any health-related queries
De-stress with Meditation Library - World’s first AI-powered meditation assistant and Sleep Music Library to relax and unwind

Read more about Dozee at https://www.dozee.io

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Introducing vaccine tracker! With a huge vaccination drive worldwide, it is important to track your health response to vaccination for proactive management. Use Dozee’s AI-powered AHI (Advanced Health Intelligence) to stay on top of your health! View your health data on the go with our interactive grid and get insights on your health at your fingertips. Instantly measure the state of your health with the different Dozee AHI card colours and get personalized alerts.

title: Dozee: Track Vitals & Sleep

creator: Turtle Shell Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Our all-new Dozee Home app allows you to stay on top of your health while you sleep! It combines science with proprietary AI algorithms to measure, analyze and track your vitals and sleep. It measures blood pressure, heart rate, respiration rate, stress and sleep in a contactless manner.
The app comes as part of the Dozee Home offering. India's 1st AI-based contactless remote health monitoring device with an early warning system. Dozee works on Ballistocardiography - a scientific method that measures the micro and macro vibrations produced by our heartbeats, respiration and body movements. Al-based algorithms analyze these micro-vibrations in the form of electric signals to monitor a person's health biomarkers on a regular basis. Dozee App enables you to configure the Dozee device and track your or your loved ones' health from anywhere in the world.
How does Dozee make health tracking easy while you sleep?
Monitors vital signs - BP, HR and RR remotely, in a contactless manner.
Gives timely life-saving notifications through the AI-based Early Warning System
Creates trends of vital signs by continuously tracking and analyzing health data
Provides automated weekly reports in an easy shareable PDF format
Enables you to share your health data with your family and loved ones
Which vitals does Dozee measure? What do they signify?
Blood Pressure (BP) - the measurement of the pressure or force of blood inside your arteries. Each time your heart beats, it pumps blood into arteries that carry blood throughout the body
Heart Rate (HR) - the number of times a heart beats per minute to indicate overall health as well as exertion levels at a particular point in time
Respiration Rate (RR) - the number of breaths you take each minute to indicate how well your heart and lungs are functioning
Stress (HRV) - a measure of the variation in time between each heartbeat. It is considered a possible marker of resilience and behavioural flexibility. As per medical literature, people who have a high HRV may have greater cardiovascular fitness and may be more resilient to stress i.e. have Low-stress levels.
Read more about Dozee at https://www.dozee.health
